---
description: Orchi desktop frontend conventions
globs: src/desktop/src/renderer/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

- Stack: React 19, TanStack Router/Query, shadcn/ui
- Import via `@/` alias only — no relative `../` across folders
- Query keys in `lib/query-keys.ts` — never inline arrays in components
- Providers in `providers/`, hooks in `hooks/` — do not mix
- API fetch in `lib/{domain}/api.ts` with `getApiBaseUrl()` and `readErrorMessage()`
- See `docs/frontend/coding-standards.md` and `docs/frontend/api-conventions.md`

## Visual / theme

- Theme = CSS variables in `assets/main.css` (`:root` / `.dark`) — that is the shadcn theme
- Fonts: DM Sans Variable (UI) + JetBrains Mono (code), self-hosted only — no Google Fonts CDN
- Prefer semantic tokens (`bg-background`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`) — no raw hex in TSX
- Neutral zinc surfaces; modest blue primary for focus/CTAs only
- Readable density: prefer `text-sm`/`text-base` for titles and body; avoid ultra-tiny primary chrome
- For UI polish / new screens, follow `.cursor/skills/orchi-ui-theme/SKILL.md`
